msgid ""
"\"%s\" is an audio CD track. \n"
"Tenacity cannot open audio CDs directly. \n"
"Extract (rip) the CD tracks to an audio format that \n"
"Tenacity can import, such as WAV or AIFF."
msgstr ""
"\"%s\" adalah trek CD audio. \n"
"Tenacity tidak dapat membuka CD audio secara langsung. \n"
"Ekstrak (rip) trek CD ke format audio yang \n"
"dapat diimpor oleh Audacity, seperti WAV atau AIFF."

