#: plug-ins/vocalrediso.ny
msgid ""
" - The two channels are identical, i.e. dual mono.\n"
"                The center can't be removed.\n"
"                Any remaining difference may be caused by lossy encoding."
msgstr ""
" - Kedua saluran identik, yaitu mono ganda.\n"
"                Pusat tidak dapat dihapus.\n"
"                Perbedaan yang tersisa mungkin disebabkan oleh pengodean "
"lossy."

#: plug-ins/vocalrediso.ny
msgid ""
" - The two Channels are strongly related, i.e. nearly mono or extremely "
"panned.\n"
"                Most likely, the center extraction will be poor."
msgstr ""
" - Kedua Saluran sangat terkait, yaitu hampir mono atau pan ekstrem.\n"
"                Kemungkinan besar, ekstraksi pusat akan buruk."

#: plug-ins/vocalrediso.ny
msgid ""
" - A fairly good value, at least stereo in average and not too wide spread."
msgstr ""
" - Nilai yang cukup baik, setidaknya stereo secara rata-rata dan tidak "
"terlalu menyebar."

#: plug-ins/vocalrediso.ny
msgid ""
" - An ideal value for Stereo.\n"
"                However, the center extraction depends also on the used "
"reverb."
msgstr ""
" - Nilai ideal untuk Stereo.\n"
"                Namun, ekstraksi pusat juga bergantung pada reverb yang "
"digunakan."

#: plug-ins/vocalrediso.ny
msgid ""
" - The two channels are almost not related.\n"
"                Either you have only noise or the piece is mastered in a "
"unbalanced manner.\n"
"                The center extraction can still be good though."
msgstr ""
" - Kedua saluran hampir tidak terkait.\n"
"                Entah Anda hanya memiliki derau atau karya ini dimaster "
"dengan cara yang tidak seimbang.\n"
"                Ekstraksi pusat tetap bisa bagus."

#: plug-ins/vocalrediso.ny
msgid ""
" - Although the Track is stereo, the field is obviously extra wide.\n"
"                This can cause strange effects.\n"
"                Especially when played by only one speaker."
msgstr ""
" - Meskipun Trek adalah stereo, bidangnya jelas ekstra lebar.\n"
"                Ini dapat menyebabkan efek yang aneh.\n"
"                Terutama saat diputar hanya oleh satu speaker."

#: plug-ins/vocalrediso.ny
msgid ""
" - The two channels are nearly identical.\n"
"                  Obviously, a pseudo stereo effect has been used\n"
"                  to spread the signal over the physical distance between "
"the speakers.\n"
"                  Don't expect good results from a center removal."
msgstr ""
" - Kedua saluran hampir identik.\n"
"                  Jelas, efek pseudo stereo telah digunakan\n"
"                  untuk menyebarkan sinyal di sepanjang jarak fisik antara "
"speaker.\n"
"                  Jangan berharap hasil yang baik dari penghapusan pusat."

#: plug-ins/vocalrediso.ny
msgid "This plug-in works only with stereo tracks."
msgstr "Plug-in ini hanya bekerja dengan trek stereo."

